## Description {#details}

This struct provides an overload for <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/castinfo">CastInfo</a> where From has <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/simplify-type">simplify&#95;type</a> defined.

This simply forwards to the appropriate <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/castinfo">CastInfo</a> with the simplified type/value, so you don&#39;t have to implement both.

Definition at line 503 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/support/casting-h">Casting.h</a>.
